        "comment": "Over a wide area 10 to 25 cm of snow has fallen. The wind was violent at times. The wind will transport the new snow significantly. <br/> The new snow and wind slabs will be deposited on the unfavourable surface of an old snowpack above the tree line. The old snowpack will be weakly bonded, especially on west, north and east facing slopes, and on south facing slopes at elevated altitudes."
